veltyJustification\":\"Added routing-specific evidence: parent aliases under-cover several foundations axes despite child-level triggers, and the requested benchmark artifact path is absent locally.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What routing changes would most improve Mode A?\",\"Can the benchmark artifact be verified locally?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What routing changes would most improve Mode A?\",\"Can the benchmark artifact be verified locally?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Treat the local 014-routing-benchmark artifact as verified evidence\",\"reason\":\"No matching path or benchmark artifact was present under the sk-design parent; the 83/100 score is operator-provided context, not a local file citation.\",\"evidence\":\"file:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/002-foundations/research/lineages/gpt55fast/iterations/iteration-002.md\"}],\"durationMs\":0,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T03:54:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104407-9dwd00\",\"generation\":1,\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rollingAvg\":null,\"madScore\":null,\"entropyCoverage\":0.5,\"compositeStop\":0.35}}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":3,\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Reference and asset usefulness\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.58,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Moved from coverage inventory to operator-use improvements: token cross-loading, register enforcement, worked examples, and sk-code handoff structure.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which references or assets would improve usefulness without duplicating basics?\",\"Where does the current workflow create friction?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Which references or assets would improve usefulness without duplicating basics?\",\"Where does the current workflow create friction?\"],\"durationMs\":0,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-27T03:54:00Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104407-9dwd00\",\"generation\":1,\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rolling